#: src/window/mod.rs:199
msgid ""
"A recording is currently in progress. Quitting immediately may cause the "
"recording to be unplayable. Please stop the recording before quitting."
msgstr ""
"Tá taifeadadh ar siúl faoi láthair. D'fhéadfadh sé nach bhféadfaí an "
"taifeadadh a sheinm má scoirtear láithreach. Stop an taifeadadh roimh scor."

#: src/window/mod.rs:202
msgid ""
"Quitting will cancel the processing and may cause the recording to be "
"unplayable."
msgstr ""
"Má scoireann tú, cuirfear an phróiseáil ar ceal agus d'fhéadfadh sé go "
"mbeifear in ann an taifeadadh a sheinm."

